<plot>Reed Hawke, CEO of Hawke Industries has decided to run for President of the United States. He has prepared a weekend get together with his family to announce his decision. He doesn't realize that his family is bitter about his decision and are willing to expose family secrets in order to prevent him from becoming a candidate. They don't realize that he is willing to do anything to keep his family silent. The player observes the events from their apartment which over looks Hawke Manor and may decide to observe or take action.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?644018</url></doc>
